## Not covered by these licences

The contents of `sources/` and `assets/` are excluded from this repository
(see `.gitignore`) and are not licensed or redistributed here.

`sources/` holds third-party upstream works. In particular, Warodai is
CC BY-NC-ND 3.0, which forbids adaptations and commercial use; its text is not
present in this repository and must not be copied, translated, or published as
part of this project. See NOTICE.

`assets/` holds generated media, which is built locally rather than
distributed here. Entries reference media by `ASSET_PATH` and record its
licence and credit in their `* Media` blocks; anyone redistributing generated
audio is responsible for meeting the terms recorded there. See NOTICE.
